
Here is a place where you can submit your coming and planned local events.
*Meetup
*Bootcamp
*Hackathons
...more !

For each events, create one folder with your event description and all the basic infos 
                + a new folder with your picture / banner
                + a new folder with your event recap (Minimum top 7 pictures) 

You can create a folder as Collaborator using : "/ " after your event name
ex: public/events/BabiCryptoDays/infos-pictures
